SELECT
  DATEFROMPARTS ( year_id, month_id, 1 ) as time,
  SUM(amount) as value
FROM
  expenses
WHERE
  expense_type_id = 10 AND DATEFROMPARTS ( year_id, month_id, 1 ) BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()
GROUP BY 
  DATEFROMPARTS ( year_id, month_id, 1 )
ORDER BY
  time ASC

       SUM(income) - (SUM(expenses) + SUM(payments)) AS Excess
FROM     dbo.View_Totals
WHERE
  DATEFROMPARTS ( year_id, month_id, 1 ) BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()
GROUP BY 
  DATEFROMPARTS ( year_id, month_id, 1 )
ORDER BY
  time ASC
